snippet.title: NUMTATE 2.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
NUMTATE is a challenging grid based puzzle game in which you move parts around by rotating, pushing and attracting them to solve numeric puzzles.

Play now:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1234160/NUMTATE/

Learn more:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Metrollos
